:131529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-29T17:09:22.000Z","msg":"每隔一年都會重睇一次 每次都有更深感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e999fed139b7e75c1d7f5c0e3ed43bd3b83a030","tid":451751,"uid":56223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:48:19.000Z","msg":"好多年前睇過頭幾集但睇唔明做咩"},{"pid":"0314ac85439504ad69aa4b016f578de433509f16","tid":451751,"uid":29863,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-30T10:51:11.000Z","msg":"終於有人講NANA <br />\n好想作者寫埋落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天堂之吻都好正<br />\n睇完結局都抑鬱左一排"}]}